snippet.title: FRAMEWORK: Found Footage - Trailer 1
snippet.description:
COMING SOON.


FRAMEWORK: Found Footage is the newest and most realistic VHS style horror game. FRAMEWORK is based on the popular internet creepypasta 'The Backrooms', popularized by Kane Pixels. The game is open world and explores many other liminal spaces. More trailers and information will be posted on this channel.

TWITTER: https://twitter.com/AdrianAfshar
